** locating via siblings following sibling (s
2 types of sibling -
1. following sibling (siblings below static element or any element are following sibling to that)
     syntax: td[text()='name']//following-sibling::td[3]
2. preceding sibling (siblings above  static element or any element are preceding sibling to that)
     syntax: td[text()='name']//preceding-sibling::td[3]